result.name: government-major-projects-portfolio-data-home-office
result.notes: Publication of Home Office Major Projects Portfolio (GMPP) data as part of the Major Projects Authority (MPA) annual report.  This includes the MPA RAG rating, departmental narrative, key project data including financial information (whole life cost, annual budget and forecast spend) and timetable. This data is 6 months in arrears and will be updated every 12 months.

organization.name: home-office
organization.title: Home Office
organization.description:
The Home Office leads on immigration and passports, drugs policy, crime policy and counter-terrorism and works to ensure visible, responsive and accountable policing in the UK.

Home Office is a ministerial department, supported by 26 agencies and public bodies.

https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/home-office
